org.apache.poi.ss.usermodel

Enum FontFamily

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<FontFamily>
      • org.apache.poi.ss.usermodel.FontFamily
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<FontFamily> 

    public enum FontFamily
extends java.lang.Enum<FontFamily>
    The font family this font belongs to. A font family is a set of fonts having common stroke width and serif characteristics. The font name overrides when there are conflicting values.(此字体所属的字体系列。字体系列是一组具有共同笔画宽度和衬线特征的字体。当存在冲突的值时，字体名称将覆盖。)
    Author:
    Gisella Bronzetti
